- PQShield — `Software Prototype Intern – Post-Quantum Cryptography` — internship scope and seniority look too junior / temporary for Jonas's profile.
- University College Cork — `PostDoc (or Research Assistant) in Privacy-enhancing Technologies` — explicit application deadline was December 19, 2025, which is already past as of March 22, 2026.
- QEDIT — `Cryptography Engineer` — already present in `shared/seen_jobs.md`.
